members.member:
Block a user for the current user account.
The user will not be able to DM the current user account.
/// or if the user is already blocked.

member.remarks:
Optionally you can also send a C# class as the json body for the request, this is useful for POST/PUT requests.


You need to interface your custom class using 

CustomClass : StoatRequest

{

    public string option = "Hi"

}

